entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning the zone for Handro's ship's signature.  Proceed to expected entry point.
entries.assassinate_success: You destroyed Handro's ship. Return to Officer M'kae for a reward.
entries.escort_remaining: You have destroyed one of the escort ships.  %DI of 5 ships remain.
entries.escort_wiped_out: The escort has been destroyed.  Eliminate Handro before he leaves the system!
entries.failed_escape: Cal Handro has left the system.  Return to Officer M'kae to report your failure.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Naboo System to intercept Cal Handro.
entries.quest_target_d: Cal Handro is finally within your grasp.  The dirty traitor will take Imperial secrets to the Rebellion if he is allowed to leave the system.  Eliminate him at all costs!
entries.title: Naboo System: Destroy Cal Handro's Ship
